metadata.description:
Immerse yourself in a new realm of music with [The Outsider Collective](https://www.theoutsidercollective.io/)'s latest mixtape, The Outsiders Volume 1. This unique offering is the result of a collaborative effort between a talented group of musicians and creatives within the web3 music space. Each track is a one-of-a-kind expression of our dedication to creativity, innovation, and experimentation, showcasing the boundless potential of collaborative music-making.

---

### Tracks

1. 1 **Today** - [sqwee](https://twitter.com/sqwee_sqwad) x [werb](https://twitter.com/YungWerb) x [KLOU](https://twitter.com/LOUNRTRIBE) x [CashiusK](https://twitter.com/k_cashius)

2. 2 **Breathe** - [74k](https://twitter.com/SVN4K) x [Eliza Rae](https://twitter.com/Sistalegz)

3. 3 **Addy (Bet It Up)** - [Divus](https://twitter.com/divusp_) x [KLOU](https://twitter.com/LOUNRTRIBE) x [PROF!T](https://twitter.com/pr0fitvsPr0phet) x [Wavezz](https://twitter.com/wavezzz777)

4. 4 **Saturday In Blue** - [illuminated](https://twitter.com/illuminatedbab3) x [werb](https://twitter.com/YungWerb) x [GRL](https://twitter.com/grlkrash)

5. 5 **Home Town** - [Sergio](https://twitter.com/Sergismooth1) x [jo.ao](https://twitter.com/juhhwow)

6. 6 **Fools Gold** - [iiiSavi](https://twitter.com/IIISavi) x [JB](https://twitter.com/JBGotGame3)

7. 7 **Cant Stay** - [paperhandpapi](https://twitter.com/papioshu) x [Omotayo](https://twitter.com/omotayo_music) x [Eligh](https://twitter.com/eligh)

8. 8 **WDYM** - [GRL](https://twitter.com/grlkrash) x [werb](https://twitter.com/YungWerb) x [3122Y342E](https://twitter.com/3122Y342E)

9. 9 **We Want More** - [Jonny October](https://twitter.com/JonnyOctober) x [KLOU](https://twitter.com/LOUNRTRIBE) x [Eligh](https://twitter.com/eligh)

10. 10 **Case Study** - [Bad Alphabet](https://twitter.com/badalphabet101) x [PROF!T](https://twitter.com/pr0fitvsPr0phet) x [Fresh Air](https://twitter.com/fa_61497)

11. 11 **Board The Plane** - [Rowe Renders](https://twitter.com/RoweRenders) x [Bad Alphabet](https://twitter.com/badalphabet101) x [werb](https://twitter.com/YungWerb)

12. 12 **Sanguinarian** - [shxdw](https://twitter.com/shxdw___) x [GRL](https://twitter.com/grlkrash) x [werb](https://twitter.com/YungWerb) x [Jadyn Violet](https://twitter.com/jadynviolet)
